    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Cords of silk or other fine material used to hang honor decorations and orders around the neck. The colors and characteristics of the cords may indicate positions and specialties.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
